  "title": "Stage manager",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Set up and manage the rehearsal space</li>\n  <li>Record blocking, timings, and director's notes</li>\n  <li>Track script and staging changes</li>\n  <li>Ensure cast attendance and punctuality</li>\n  <li>Maintain clear communication between director and departments</li>\n  <li>Monitor safety and working conditions</li>\n  <li>Coordinate prop and costume needs for rehearsal</li>\n  <li>Call the show (lighting, sound, set, etc.) via headset</li>\n  <li>Ensure all cues are executed on time and correctly</li>\n  <li>Manage backstage activity and scene transitions</li>\n  <li>Handle emergencies or performance disruptions</li>\n  <li>Write and distribute daily performance reports</li>\n  <li>Maintain cast and crew morale and discipline</li>\n</ul>",
